{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ecdca7c187","title":"毛泽东转发联运党委关于开展三反斗争情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f8be2226a","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":24,"articleId":"ecdca7c187"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"87f421623f","type":"title","text":"毛泽东转发联运党委关于开展三反斗争情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ecdca7c187"},{"id":"139ed0ff39","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ecdca7c187"},{"id":"45ec369cc6","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区并转所属各单位；志愿军；并告各中央局：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ecdca7c187"},{"id":"b5363b9c1d","type":"paragraph","text":"联运党委这个报告很好，请你们参酌办理，并在党内刊物上发表。有些人以为开展三反斗争须要很长的时间，这是不对的。除复杂案件外，每一机关部队有半个月至多一个月就够了。联运党委所规定的时间不到一个月，这是很对的。如果铁道兵团在朝鲜那样每天受轰炸和极为紧张的工作情况下能够这样做，那么国内的机关部队为什么不能这样做呢？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ecdca7c187"},{"id":"22ffdb13e1","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十二月二十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ecdca7c187"}],"page":{"id":"e27136c0cc","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ecdca7c187","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}